      "id": "luz2v48g",
      "questionNumber": 6,
      "questionText": "<p>For the given compounds, the correct order of increasing $$\\mathrm{pK}_{\\mathrm{a}}$$ value :</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://app-content.cdn.examgoal.net/fly/@width/image/1luz16fu5/39f3956e-bcfe-4a6d-b3a9-5f7867bf7d02/2645c5d0-fa18-11ee-b660-8fcb8bd681fc/file-1luz16fu6.png?format=png\" data-orsrc=\"https://app-content.cdn.examgoal.net/image/1luz16fu5/39f3956e-bcfe-4a6d-b3a9-5f7867bf7d02/2645c5d0-fa18-11ee-b660-8fcb8bd681fc/file-1luz16fu6.png\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"max-width:100%;height:auto;display:block;margin:0 auto;max-height:40vh;vertical-align:baseline\" alt=\"JEE Main 2024 (Online) 9th April Morning Shift Chemistry - Basics of Organic Chemistry Question 84 English\"></p>\n<p>Choose the correct answer from the options given below :</p>",
